<div style="max-width:740px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem">
  <h1 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:1.5rem">About NickPicks</h1>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;line-height:1.75;font-size:1.125rem">NickPicks is a product review site run by Nick, a home office enthusiast who tests and curates the best gear so you can skip the guesswork and get back to doing what you love.</p>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;line-height:1.75">I started NickPicks after spending years buying the wrong things — too many underpowered monitors, chairs that hurt after three hours, and kitchen gadgets that lived in a drawer after one use. The problem wasn't a lack of reviews online. It was a lack of honest ones. Most review sites are either content farms churning out SEO copy or undisclosed paid placements. I wanted something different: real picks from someone who actually cares.</p>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;line-height:1.75">Today, NickPicks covers five categories where I spend my own money and time: <a href="{{ '/categories/home-office/' | url }}">home office</a>, <a href="{{ '/categories/fitness/' | url }}">fitness</a>, <a href="{{ '/categories/kitchen/' | url }}">kitchen</a>, <a href="{{ '/categories/luxury-beauty/' | url }}">beauty</a>, and <a href="{{ '/categories/pet-tech/' | url }}">pet tech</a>. Each guide is based on hands-on research — not generic specs copy-pasted from a manufacturer's page.</p>

  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">How I Review Products</h2>
  <ul style="margin:0.75rem 0 1rem 1.5rem;line-height:1.75">
    <li><strong>Hands-on testing</strong> — I use the products I write about in my own home office setup before recommending them.</li>
    <li><strong>Verified buyer reviews</strong> — I cross-reference hundreds of Amazon ratings and long-term ownership reviews to catch patterns a short test won't reveal.</li>
    <li><strong>Spec comparison</strong> — I compare manufacturer specs, warranty terms, and pricing across multiple retailers to ensure you're getting real value.</li>
    <li><strong>Commission-free ranking</strong> — Products are ranked by real-world value, not by which one pays a higher affiliate rate. Some of my top picks carry lower commissions than alternatives I ranked below them.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
  <p style="line-height:1.75">NickPicks participates in the Amazon Associates Program and other affiliate programs. We may earn commissions when you buy through our links — at no extra cost to you. This never influences our rankings or recommendations. See our full <a href="{{ '/affiliate-disclosure/' | url }}">affiliate disclosure</a>.</p>

  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">Get in Touch</h2>
  <p style="line-height:1.75">Have a product you think I should cover, or want to work together? <a href="{{ '/contact/' | url }}">Reach out on the contact page</a> — I read every email.</p>
